', 'Phenelzine, Tranylcypromine, Maprotiline, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Trazodone, More', 'Tinidazole, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Dexlansoprazole, Rifabutin', 1767369485);
